{"tid":2052140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"銀髮族拒屈服 撐青年抗爭","createTime":"2020-06-05T09:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T09:55:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee41ba6e19c2c7b6682afd64116833b345d4273","tid":2052140,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:47:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200605/QWPF3EMAH6PP3JBS5FCO43JFIM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200605%2FQWPF3EMAH6PP3JBS5FCO43JFIM%2F&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=c56acd48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200605%2FQWPF3EMAH6PP3JBS5FCO43JFIM%2F&h=f9141a67\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200605/QWPF3EMAH6PP3JBS5FCO43JFIM/</a><br />\n<br />\n銀髮族拒屈服 撐青年抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SAZZhNWLeIqXYI6a5Aki1g1ItTc=/802x531/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O3AYW7KEWOJ7QPNFOWRHB2ZRB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSAZZhNWLeIqXYI6a5Aki1g1ItTc%3D%2F802x531%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO3AYW7KEWOJ7QPNFOWRHB2ZRB4.jpg&h=be0dfe10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥氏夫婦今年選擇在觀塘悼念。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】參與各區六四悼念活動的市民，當中不少是銀髮族，部份市民更是六四事件至今，31年以來年年都參與，對今年未能在維園舉行悼念活動，有市民稱不代表向政權屈服，反而認同遍地開花在各區悼念，代表「我哋有個心喺度」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警屯重兵動口不動手  為惡法製和平假象<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「悼念永遠在心裏面」<br />\n<br />\n從第一年起已參與六四悼念集會的麥氏夫婦，今年六四31周年亦沒缺席，兩人參加昨晚在觀塘海濱公園的悼念活動。。。。。。。。。。。。謂「悼念永遠在心裏面」。<br />\n<br />\n過去每年都參加維園燭光晚會的銀髮族陳先生，今年因限聚令未。。。。。。。。。哋有個心喺度，最重要係有個心喺度」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎敬中、黃麗英"},{"pid":"e6b7a82bbe844e3af43fb18d203613b796cc307d","tid":2052140,"uid":59922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:49:12.000Z","msg":"respect"},{"pid":"1c9421faefff3e6414e0300cd8a94424bbfcfc0c","tid":2052140,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:50:08.000Z","msg":"睇親呢d再對比番屋企個深藍老<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />..."},{"pid":"cea174a6ec7c944a5cbdb11a25b905630fdce0f6","tid":2052140,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c9421faefff3e6414e0300cd8a94424bbfcfc0c","tid":2052140,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:50:08.000Z","msg":"睇親呢d再對比番屋企個深藍老<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:51:37.000Z","msg":"盡左力都改變唔到佢地就算啦"},{"pid":"5cff27b72647fa1467d97283f552e5b673f6f0cb","tid":2052140,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:52:43.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b88fe096e37bcb230565bef72fd4ee422919ae8","tid":2052140,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:55:09.000Z","msg":"同食神一樣, 只要用心就可以平反64, 只要用心就可以推翻中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}